readable.content: People are riding on a ride at a theme park or carnival . Riders in the log ride throw their arms in the air in enjoyment as they prepare for the watery descent . Two people are riding down a log flume in a theme park . Two people raise up their arms in a rollercoaster ride Water log amusement park ride with people in it at night .
